(101, 1, '2023-01-26 07:52:29', '2023-01-26 07:52:29', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":77,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/witch-1024x576.jpe\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-77\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Mobile Suit Gundam: the Witch from Mercury</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With the end of season 1, Mobile suit Gundam: the Witch from Mercury was a huge success as it introduce new people to the Gundam franchise and entertain old Gundam fans. The animation studio announced that a second season was in production and will likely be air in April 2023.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:post-date /-->', 'Gundam Anime Season 2 coming soon', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '64-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-01-26 07:52:29', '2023-01-26 07:52:29', '', 64, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=101', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(102, 1, '2023-01-26 07:53:19', '2023-01-26 07:53:19', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":80,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/char.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-80\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Hyaku-Shiki Potato Chips (Curry)</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In December 2022, Hyaku-Shiki Potato chips (Curry) makes a return. For a limited time, people will be able enjoy this chips at a discount for there will be a sale during December.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:post-date /-->', 'Return of the Hyaku-Shiki Potato Chips (2023)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '74-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-01-26 07:53:19', '2023-01-26 07:53:19', '', 74, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=102', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(103, 1, '2023-01-26 07:53:56', '2023-01-26 07:53:56', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>New Grade</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":83,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/free-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-83\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">MGSD Freedom Gundam</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In 2022, Bandai announced a new line of Gunpla called Master Grade Super Deformed (MGSD). The first model will be the Freedom Gundam and is reported to be released in January 2023 for $96.33 ($SD).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:post-date /-->', 'Gunpla 2023', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '71-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-01-26 07:53:56', '2023-01-26 07:53:56', '', 71, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=103', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
